Bilazea template is a PHP/AJAX/HTML template used in several sites.

It's currently an 'on working' project, a prototype. First official release will be available in December.

Main demonstration can be seen on Bilazea.com, on page http://bilazea.com/projects/BILAZEA_template

It is a very simple framework designed to create quickly a website.
- Main language used is PHP, to create navigation stuff mainly
- MOOTOOLS (http://github.com/mootools/mootools-core), XHTML and CSS are used to present content
